                          Shift      Shift  
                     Shift+solo      NoAction      
                         Option      Option        
                        Control      Control
                Control+Track        GoZone HomePeek
                            Alt      Alt 
                            Zoom     Zoom   
                  GlobalView         Global 
                          Scrub      Scrub
                          
//ZOOM TO ITEM AND INTO ITEMFADES ZONE
                          
 
Zoom     Reaper  _SWS_ITEMZOOM // SWS: Zoom to selected items
Zoom      GoZone ItemFades

